headline: Church & Dwight: Hammered Down As Expected, Upgrading To Hold
summary: Church & Dwight posts robust Q3 with 5% growth, strong volumes, raised guidance and cost control plus buybacks and acq. Read why CHD stock is upgraded to a hold.
